About us

  • Architecture Studio
  • Interior design
  • 3D modeling & Animation
  • Decoration & Furniture
  • High Performance
SEECA Design Studio is a landscape design and construction firm based in Portland, Oregon that creates residential outdoor living spaces and gardens. We strive to create meaningful spaces that fulfill our clients visions and function great for years to come.
Our mission is on bringing a balance of healthy, beautiful living spaces to our clients.
